"breadcrumbs" : "Sysdig Documentation \/ Sysdig Secure \/ Policies \/ Understanding Sysdig Secure Rules \/ Fast Rules \/ Network Rules", 
"snippet" : "These rules are used to: Detect activity on ports outside a trusted list on a specific list Notify in case of unexpected inbound\/outbound connections...", 
