"snippet" : "When you drill down into the Scan Results list, the details menu provides a variety of ways to view vulnerability and policy violation data at a glance. Policy Summary views Vulnerabilities summaries Content summaries These summaries provide: An easy-to-parse view of why a specific image failed Whic...", 
