"breadcrumbs" : "Sysdig Documentation \/ Sysdig Platform \/ On-Premises Deployments \/ On-Premises Installation \/ Manual Installation (OpenShift) \/ Set Up (OpenShift) \/ Prerequisites \/ DNS Preparation \/ Option 1: DNS without Wildcard", 
"snippet" : "You need to request two different DNS records from your DNS team: one for the Sysdig API\/UI and another for the Sysdig collector. These records should point to your infrastructure nodes and are the two routes that will be exposed, i.e., sysdig.api.example.com and sysdig.collector.example.com ....", 
