"snippet" : "To upgrade from v. 1091 > v. 2435, you would: Upgrade to v. 1149, using the Migration Tool for Unified Events and the Basic Upgrade instructions. Then upgrade to v. 1765, using the Migration Tool for Connector and the appropriate Expanded Upgrade instructions. Finally upgrade to v. 2435, using the B...", 
