"url" : "upgrade-replicated-installations.html#UUID-3f5c6850-00ab-ef04-df04-9ad3d8f22296_UUID-c50dab71-dc51-50d0-6377-fc2843f3754c", 
"breadcrumbs" : "Sysdig Documentation \/ Sysdig Platform \/ On-Premises Deployments \/ On-Premises Upgrades \/ Upgrade Replicated Installations \/ Non-Airgapped Installation \/ Upgrade Replicated Components \/ Check Current Version", 
"snippet" : "The Replicated infrastructure installs its own container based agents that deploy and manage the various Sysdig back-end components. To confirm the currently running version of the Replicated agent, perform replicated --version at the command line on each host. [ Reference Replicated.com]...", 
