"breadcrumbs" : "Sysdig Documentation \/ Sysdig Integrations \/ Integrate Applications (Default App Checks) \/ HAProxy \/ Sysdig Agent Configuration \/ Example: Collect HAProxy Stats by UNIX Socket", 
