"snippet" : "Review how to Edit dragent.yaml to Integrate or Modify Application Checks . There is no default configuration for MySQL, as a unique user and password are required for metrics polling. Add the entry for MySQL into dragent.yaml , updating the user and pass field credentials. app_checks: - name: mysql...", 
